  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSV_header_row
    describes the head line (the labels) on the input file, it contains private Strings that matching the labels on the original file, getters of the values and one constructor that gets the relevant values from the header line.
    CSV_Merged_Row
    this class represents a row from Union output file.
    CSV_row
    describes the structure of the rows in input files.
    DateFormat  
    Full_Coordinate
    this class represents coordinate that include altitude, longitude and latitude and also MAC's signal of this coordinate.
    toCSVtoKML
    in this class we define List variable that gets data from input file, and List that gets data that will appear on output file.
